 } } \right| + \left| {\matrix{
   4 &amp; 3 &amp; 1  \cr 
   6 &amp; 6 &amp; 1  \cr 
   3 &amp; 5 &amp; 1  \cr 

 } } \right|} \right]$$<br><br>$$ = {1 \over 2}[\{ 1(3 - 5) - 2(4 - 3) + 1(20 - 9)\}  + \{ 4(6 - 5) - 3(6 - 3) + 1(30 - 18)\} ]$$<br><br>$$ = {1 \over 2}[7 + 7] = {{14} \over 2} = 7$$ sq. units

